{"type": "article", "id": 13206, "title": "烤鸭店怎么装修才合适？这家店把笔筒挂满了天花板", "description": "书房用具出现在了餐厅里，显得有些拥挤。", "date": "2015-08-10T12:06:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14192, "name": "烤鸭店"}, {"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 14193, "name": "天津餐厅"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071106482WC6TBfieGKAcrY4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t近日，设计事务所<a href=\"http://www.golucci.com/User/index.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">古鲁奇</a>在天津开发区完成了烤鸭店“泰钰丰”的设计。这虽然是个餐厅，却使用了书写元素——大量的笔筒挂满了天花板，还挺壮观，墙四面则是以中国蓝百宝格为背景的装饰架。但是整体风格显得有些拥挤。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110644CGAt0Ooc3B4NxfLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"text-align:left;\" data-ratio=\"0.9375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t远望店铺\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110644UG8OrfnSK5h3H7pl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.459375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t蓝百宝阁\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110644RLvJpVz0BcZ9P5Qt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t另外一个角度\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t店内的餐桌分为几种，多人餐桌使用的是软座，小桌配备的则是硬质的椅子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110645vdaK9csQgqPn8FMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t中式风\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110645toPg8OGhx1N4dDiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t另外一侧\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071106463kW0jBVrSt42JTcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t下图是笔筒装饰的细节\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110646cp48oSJtYA5HfnPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.golucci.com/User/index.aspx\">古鲁奇</a></span>设计事务所主要从事餐厅设计，还完成过其他一些项目\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110647QRJXZCAN6HuV9l2W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t烧肉达人店铺设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110647ueERpMTdgLqyGYzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t721 幸福牧场\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071106483t6sdv5mISPnjR1y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t又及餐厅\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><em><a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/peking-duck-restaurant-golucci.htm\" target=\"_blank\">gooood</a></em>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}